# Get input
n, m, x, y = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
x_list = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
y_list = [int(i) for i in input().split()]

# Check if war will break out
if all(x < z <= y for z in x_list + y_list) and all(z > x for z in x_list) and all(z <= y for z in y_list):
    print('No War')
else:
    print('War')

def main():
    n, m, x, y = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    xs = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    ys = [int(x) for x in input().split()]

    # X < Z \leq Y
    # x_1, x_2, ..., x_N < Z
    # y_1, y_2, ..., y_M \geq Z
    z = min(y, min(xs))
    if x < z <= y and all(x < z for x in xs) and all(z <= y for y in ys):
        print("No War")
    else:
        print("War")

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
